article_text:
(Best of the tube this weekend: Catch us on Fox News Channel’s “The Journal Editorial Report” discussing the Supreme Court term just ended. Saturday at 3 p.m. ET, with a repeat showing Sunday at 3 p.m.) If Hillary Clinton answered questions, here’s one we’d like to ask her: Do you believe the Little Sisters of the Poor should be compelled to change their religious beliefs?

That question has arisen over the past few weeks, to the consternation of some of Mrs. Clinton’s supporters. She and her campaign have not addressed...
